review:
Several drawbacks:
1. Authentification by sms - when creating an account, it goes into a loop with the whole phone confirmation. It took me 10 minutes to get it right, and I can’t even remember how I did so that I can advise others;
2. Filters / sort - no possibility to sort your food by the quickes options or the best rated, it just seems the restaurants are randomly shown in your feed (except the paid advertising, which takes the hot spot).

